<td class="image-box-image" style="width: 195px; text-align: center;"><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Ls52XZ6OVCk/US2W4agXz1I/AAAAAAAAAkg/3tBwpBJKX3M/s1600/obama_poster_shhh-e1350614107665.jpg"><img src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Ls52XZ6OVCk/US2W4agXz1I/AAAAAAAAAkg/3tBwpBJKX3M/s1600/obama_poster_shhh-e1350614107665.jpg" title="" style="border:1px solid #999;" alt="Image Unavailable" width="195px" class="image" /></a></td>
